cdata.name: AltoCar
cdata.desc: Alto Car connects passengers and drivers with the ability to add drivers to their favourites list. AltoCar has carried out more than 90,000 trips which is equivalent to 1.35 million kilometers. It has 8000 employees and a database of over 5,000 drivers generating a revenue of $500,000. The funds raised from the ICO will help expand to over 13 cities in Russia.
